---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Midcopy from '../components/Midcopy.astro';
import LeftCopyModule from '../components/LeftCopyModule.astro';
import RightCopyModule from '../components/RightCopyModule.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home - Scry">
	<main class="main">
    <Hero />
    <Midcopy />
    <LeftCopyModule desc="Who needs a CTA when you have pretty pictures?" img="https://picsum.photos/320/320"/>
    <RightCopyModule desc="This is definitely not a CTA, but by reading it, you have made it one" img="https://picsum.photos/320/320" />
    <section>
      <div data-content-region="home-reviews"></div>
    </section>
    <LeftCopyModule desc="Are we there yet?" img="https://picsum.photos/320/320"/>
    <RightCopyModule desc="Get these monkey-fighting snakes off this monday-to-friday plane!" img="https://picsum.photos/320/320" />
    <section class="w-full bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-prose mx-auto py-8 px-4">
        <p class="mb-4">Introducing ConvertoVelo, the cutting-edge digital solution that will transform the way you do business. With ConvertoVelo, your challenges will become opportunities, your sluggish processes will reach warp speed, and your conversion rates will soar beyond your wildest dreams.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Imagine a world where your problems are mere stepping stones to success. ConvertoVelo's advanced algorithms and AI-driven insights will identify bottlenecks and inefficiencies in your operations, turning them into strategic advantages. No more wasted time, no more missed opportunities.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Speed is the name of the game, and ConvertoVelo is the champion. Our lightning-fast data processing, real-time analytics, and instant decision-making capabilities will leave your competitors in the dust. You'll be making critical business decisions at the speed of thought, staying one step ahead of the competition at all times.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">But that's not all! ConvertoVelo's customer-centric approach will have your customers flocking to your business like never before. Our personalized recommendation engine, seamless user experience, and 24/7 support will make your customers feel like royalty. Watch your conversion rates skyrocket as customers not only convert but also become loyal brand advocates.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">Don't miss out on the revolution. Join the ranks of industry leaders who have already experienced the ConvertoVelo advantage. Say goodbye to problems, embrace speed, and witness customer conversion rates that defy belief. Your success story starts here with ConvertoVelo.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <LeftCopyModule desc="You don't have to take our word for it, but you probably should" img="https://picsum.photos/320/320"/>
    <div id="wavy-bg" class="h-64"></div>
    <section data-content-region="footer-social--global"></section>
	</main>
</Layout>
<style>
  #wavy-bg {
    --s: 100px; /* control the size */
    --c1: #7494EA;
    --c2: #212123;

    --_g:#0000, #0004 5%,
        var(--c2) 6%  14%,var(--c1) 16% 24%,var(--c2) 26% 34%,var(--c1) 36% 44%,
        var(--c2) 46% 54%,var(--c1) 56% 64%,var(--c2) 66% 74%,var(--c1) 76% 84%,
        var(--c2) 86% 94%,#0004 95%,#0000;
    background:
      radial-gradient(100% 50% at 100% 0   ,var(--_g)),
      radial-gradient(100% 50% at 0    50% ,var(--_g)),
      radial-gradient(100% 50% at 100% 100%,var(--_g));
    background-size: var(--s) calc(2*var(--s));
    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    background-attachment: fixed;
  }
</style>
